    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const rawText = $('Code').first().json.raw_text;\n\nconst prompt = `You are a JSON generator. You must return only valid JSON, nothing else.\n\nGiven this text message:\n${rawText.slice(0, 3000)}\n\nReturn a JSON object with exactly these fields:\n- title: a short 5-7 word title summarising what this is about\n- summary: a comprehensive summary of 3-8 sentences that captures all key points, main ideas, and important details from the text. Do not truncate or oversimplify — preserve the substance of the original message.\n- tags: array of 2-4 topic tags in lowercase\n- content_type: one of these exact strings: \"note\", \"article\", \"tutorial\", \"news\", \"concept\", \"opinion\"\n\nRules:\n- All string values must be in double quotes\n- No trailing commas\n- No text outside the JSON object\n- The summary must be self-contained — the user should not need to refer back to the original text\n\nExample output:\n{\n  \"title\": \"Short descriptive title here\",\n  \"summary\": \"Comprehensive multi-sentence summary that captures all key points and details from the original message without losing important context or nuance.\",\n  \"tags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\"],\n  \"content_type\": \"note\"\n}`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    model: \"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\n    messages: [\n      {\n        role: \"user\",\n        content: prompt\n      }\n    ],\n    temperature: 0.3\n  }\n}];"
      },
