    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const title = $json.title;\nconst content = $json.content;\nconst source = $json.source;\n\nconst prompt = `You are a JSON generator. You must return only valid JSON, nothing else.\n\nGiven this content:\nTitle: ${title}\nFull Content: ${content}\nSource: ${source}\n\nReturn a JSON object with exactly these fields:\n- summary: string, 1-3 clean sentences, must be in double quotes\n- tags: array of 2-4 lowercase topic tag strings\n- content_type: one of these exact strings: \"tutorial\", \"news\", \"tool\", \"concept\", \"case-study\", \"opinion\"\n\nRules:\n- All string values must be in double quotes\n- No trailing commas\n- No text outside the JSON object\n- Base your summary and tags on the full content, not just the title\n\nExample output:\n{\n  \"summary\": \"A brief description of the content in one sentence.\",\n  \"tags\": [\"tag1\", \"tag2\"],\n  \"content_type\": \"news\"\n}`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    model: \"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\n    messages: [\n      {\n        role: \"user\",\n        content: prompt\n      }\n    ],\n    temperature: 0.3\n  }\n}];"
      },
